text.tspan: Private civil liberties weighted by population, World, 1800 to 2022
Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem. It captures the extent to which people are free from forced
labor, have property rights, and enjoy the freedoms of movement and religion. The variables ranges from 0 to 1
Source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); Gapminder (v6); HYDE (v3.2); UN (2022)
